  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3967076356">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3967076356" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3967076356" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3967076356">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/220138476/">YoursAli</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3967076356">2023-10-19 16:33:16</a>
          <span class="comment-location">广东</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">读的第一本格拉斯家族的读物，读完另两本之后觉得此书是格拉斯家族思想的最凝练的集大成之作，回温时甚是亲切。最后一篇《泰迪》，简直是和鲜少有正面描写的西摩的直接对话，结局意料之外却在情理之中，和首篇形成呼应，圆满。真是极好的短篇集，每篇都让人耳目一新，很惊喜。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/2161892/?comment_id=3967076356"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
