  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3959261357">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3959261357" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3959261357" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3959261357">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/170429966/">Otter&#39;s moon</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3959261357">2023-10-15 23:00:01</a>
          <span class="comment-location">四川</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">和中学时期读《麦田里的守望者》很不一样了，可能因为我的思想多了一些邪恶阴暗？感觉多懂塞林格一点了。能掉入他编织的故事网里真好，虽然看得时候还是感到晕晕乎乎的，不过老是会在某一时刻又开始想“他到底想说什么？”这就是塞林格的魅力吧！最喜欢香蕉鱼和笑面人！《特迪》的结尾是最让我茫然的，看了别人的解读才知道原来结尾是他死了（我还以为是妹妹，肤浅如我）。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/2161892/?comment_id=3959261357"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="3951433491">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-3951433491" class="vote-count">0</span>
              <a id="btn-3951433491" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="3951433491">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/82241728/">不安的树</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3951433491">2023-10-04 08:41:27</a>
          <span class="comment-location">北京</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">塞林格后期的创作都称得上伟大，他和与他有共同追求的创作者树立的标准，至今无可超越。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/2161892/?comment_id=3951433491"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

      </ul>
  </div>

        

